  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin: 0px auto;padding: 24px 20px 48px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;overflow-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天下午我纯用小龙虾，不用电脑，做了一个公众号排版工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5314814814814814\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017654\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ffdcd4e0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbMwkkcylEroPUfEd2WeK40G5BAg6IB2tHANPydVBALpGv5bY52ArPuia1NE6iaGib1PyCW0GClfK9I2UvdibGibfqC4b7SNr9ZFJg0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">欢迎体验！欢迎提PR。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;color: rgb(102, 102, 102) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://publish.raphael.app\" target=\"_blank\">https://publish.raphael.app</a></span></em></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么要做？</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前我写公众号，总是在飞书或者Notion里写，然后使用某位我喜欢的知名自媒体博主的公众号排版工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">后来发现他的工具有一些bug，想改。但是再看了一下他的开源代码，呃，代码质量有点太拉了，所有的逻辑全部在一个大文件里，有点下不了手。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">正好最近玩小龙虾写代码，就试试让小龙虾自己写了算了。也顺便测试一下Gemini-3.1 Pro的审美能力。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">小龙虾写代码的细节</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 16px 0px;padding-left: 28px;list-style-position: outside;list-style-type: disc !important;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">授权了我的Github账号。</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">小龙虾自动指挥使用我系统内的多种AI Agent</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <ul style=\"margin: 16px 0px;padding-left: 28px;list-style-position: outside;list-style-type: circle !important;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">Opus 4.6</span><span leaf=\"\">：写开发计划、写逻辑代码</span></span></li>\n     <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">GPT-5.3-Codex</span><span leaf=\"\">：审核代码、做单元测试</span></span></li>\n     <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 700;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\">Gemini-3.1-Pro</span><span leaf=\"\">： 设计界面、写前端代码、设计主题风格、做端到端自动测试验证（使用browser-use）</span></span></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从提交记录里，好像只能看到Claude Code，看不到另外两位。这是因为Claude Code比较不要脸，默认情况是只要它参与了，就会在提交者里加上它自己。另外两位大哥不像这样刷存在感。</span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23425925925925925\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017651\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c291ad3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbP49PY003wYic9y8RP6LME0OA6gVfbfYSaeSpnYQtF0TJibh5HMzkglAiclf0jdAgmZUHXpIPQlLBEwXbCgWTsibs3mGAAibZyCfFYo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;margin: 32px 0px 14px;padding-left: 12px;border-left: 4px solid rgb(215, 26, 27);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;line-height: 1.35 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有哪些功能？</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 16px 0px;padding-left: 28px;list-style-position: outside;list-style-type: disc !important;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">30套由Gemini-3.1-Pro精心打磨的主题风格。在列表里就显示出了颜色配置，在你选择之前，就能知道大概。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9768518518518519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;width: 100%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22) 0px 16px 34px, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12) 0px 4px 10px;border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);margin: 30px auto !important;padding: 8px !important;border-radius: 14px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017652\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bf43642&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq6aOmBZKAbNrW5QUm3Z29Tfg5x4FGexdtyS45sRuJ1C1icddXuSvfuaSpOXV13xicwDibnY8tEbj2bowKhUAmotkqB2s63QI7icbL2ggoOicVVGE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 16px 0px;padding-left: 28px;list-style-position: outside;list-style-type: disc !important;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: rgb(215, 26, 27) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从任何富文本工具（包括飞书文档、Notion、甚至网页）直接复制</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，粘贴即自动净化为Markdown。</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 8px 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\"><